# duti configuration - Default applications for file types
# Format: bundle_id|UTI_or_extension|role
# role can be: all, viewer, editor (all = both viewer & editor)
#
# To find bundle IDs:
# mdls -name kMDItemCFBundleIdentifier /Applications/AppName.app
#
# Common UTIs:
# - public.plain-text
# - public.shell-script
# - public.python-script
# - public.folder
# - .sh, .py, .js, .ts, .json, .yaml, .md, .txt (file extensions)

